			<p class=""><a href="https://www.lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/93.13?lang=eng#12" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Doctrine and Covenants 93:13</a>.</p>
		</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote6-12461_000_042"><a name="6-12461_000_042"> </a>
