			</span>
			<p class=""><a href="https://www.lds.org/scriptures/nt/eph/4.11-13?lang=eng#10" onclick="newWindow(this.href); return false;">Ephesians 4:11–13</a>.</p>
		</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote9-12461_000_042"><a name="9-12461_000_042"> </a>
			<span class="label">
